insights.title: The Invisible 47%
insights.text: Initially, 7,549 crashes had NO location data. That's 47.5% of the dataset flying under the radar.

insights.title: Ghost Dimensions
insights.text: We found 3,500 records dated in the future (2026). A database migration error we've now flagged.

insights.title: Regex Rescue
insights.text: Using pattern matching on raw text fields, we recovered 24,500 coordinates that GPS sensors missed.

insights.title: Severity Unlocked
insights.text: We engineered a 'Severity Score' to identify high-risk zones, weighting fatalities 5x more than injuries.

insights.title: Vision Zero Impact
insights.text: Our model projects a 30% reduction in fatalities by targeting these newly discovered blackspots.
